<P>This is the text of the bill enacted by the Georgia legislature criminalizing use of 
pseudonyms and anonymous messsaging in online communication. </P> 

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT> 
<PRE>  
  
GEORGIANET 
 
GEORGIANET AUTHORITY 
 
Georgia Legislative Information 
 
HB 1630 
 
Computer or telephone network; transmitting misleading data (3.7K)  
 
*** BILL STATUS *** 
 
04/04/96 
 
HB 1630 
 
Computer or telephone network; 
transmitting misleading data 
 
1. Parsons  40th 
 
2. Scoggins  24th 
 
3. Coker  31st 
 
House Comm: Ind 
 
Senate Comm: ST&I 
 
House Vote: Yeas 142   Nays 26 
 
Senate Vote: Yeas 48  Nays 0 
 
