13. Memorandum from Paul Davis to U.S.
Representative Nancy Johnson Re: Donald G. Jones
activity in Speaker's office, March 14, 1996. See
Attachment #9. The "attached Jones memo" referred to by
Paul Davis is the June 3O, 1995 memorandum by Donald
Jones titled "Six Months of Newt's '95 revolution" which
is included in Attachment # 1.

14. Damon Chappie and Juliet Eilperin, "Jones Offered
Gingrich Campaign Giver's View on Internet
Regulation." Roll Call, April 22, 1996. Attachment # 10
